org.openehealth.ipf.commons.ihe.xds.core.ebxml

Interface EbXMLQueryResponse

  • All Superinterfaces:
    EbXMLObjectContainer, EbXMLRegistryResponse
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EbXMLQueryResponse21, EbXMLQueryResponse30

    public interface EbXMLQueryResponse
extends EbXMLObjectContainer, EbXMLRegistryResponse
    Encapsulation of the ebXML classes for AdhocQueryResponse.

    This class contains convenience methods and provides a version independent abstraction of the ebXML data structure.

    Author:
    Jens Riemschneider
